- Cybersecurity is an economic game
- Defenders need to spend less money than they will lose by getting attacked
- Attackers need to spend less money than the attack will cost them

example in antivirus EDR - lots of heavy processing options that are high efficacy but expensive https://blog.deeb.ch/posts/how-edr-works/?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email#av-emulation 